TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Q7wNt8jmuQCq6gwF8SO3V
SUMMARY:CPR\\\, First Aid & HIV Certification
DTSTAMP:20260320T020834Z
DTSTART:20260321T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Learn first aid\\\, infant\\\, child and adult CPR\\\, HIV and 
	bloodborne pathogens\\\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. Mee
	ts L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \\
	nCan you provide first aid in emergencies\\\, locate and take care of inju
	ries\\\, help a choking infant or child and stop cardiac arrest? Learn fir
	st aid\\\, infant\\\, child and adult CPR\\\, HIV and bloodborne pathogens
	\\\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. \\nModified to meet COV
	ID-19 safety requirements (hands-on only\\\, no mouth-to mouth). \\nMeets 
	L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \\nTa
	ught by Ken Norris\\\, Retired Firefighter. \\nLocation: Upper Blue Buildi
	ng\\\, Room 7.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/cpr-first-aid-hiv-ce
	rtification-4/\n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/cpr-first-aid-hiv-certification-4/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus\\\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\
	\\, 98103\\\, United States
